SDK Adapters — layer ponte critico
GPMFAdapter: TelemetryData (AoS Double) → SensorDataBuffers (SoA Float). Wrappa GPMFExtractor.extract() in async.
FITAdapter: FitMessages.recordMesgs → time series. Conversione semicircles→degrees (× 180.0 / 2^31), Garmin epoch offset (631065600s).
CSVAdapter: NKEmpowerSession, NKSpeedCoachSession → canali SoA per-stroke.
Verifica
Unit test per ogni strategia sync con dati sintetici
ComplementaryFilter: step input → convergenza attesa
Integration: pipeline completa con dati realistici, stroke count fisiologicamente plausibile
Coverage target: >90%
